  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "解一个方程，本质上是在问：什么样的x能让式子等于零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "把多项式画成一条曲线，方程的解就藏在图里。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.61,
      "size": 25776,
      "text": "曲线每一次穿过x轴的地方，就是一个实根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-1",
      "filename": "count-cnt-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/count-cnt-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.38,
      "size": 38016,
      "text": "代数基本定理告诉我们，n次多项式在复数范围恰好有n个根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-2",
      "filename": "count-cnt-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/count-cnt-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "二次方程有两个根，三次有三个，四次有四个，一个都不多不少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "count",
      "line_id": "cnt-3",
      "filename": "count-cnt-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/count-cnt-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33984,
      "text": "只不过这些根里，有的落在实数轴上，有的藏进了复数平面。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "complex",
      "line_id": "cpx-1",
      "filename": "complex-cpx-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/complex-cpx-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "曲线与x轴的交点，就是我们能直接看到的实根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "complex",
      "line_id": "cpx-2",
      "filename": "complex-cpx-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/complex-cpx-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "如果曲线悬在轴上方或下方不肯相交，那对应的就是一对共轭复根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "complex",
      "line_id": "cpx-3",
      "filename": "complex-cpx-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/complex-cpx-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "实系数多项式的复根总是成对出现，就像一对影子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "numeric",
      "line_id": "num-1",
      "filename": "numeric-num-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/numeric-num-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "高于四次的方程没有通用求根公式，我们改用数值方法逼近。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "numeric",
      "line_id": "num-2",
      "filename": "numeric-num-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/numeric-num-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.23,
      "size": 35712,
      "text": "二分法盯住符号变化的区间，不断对半夹逼，把根越关越紧。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "numeric",
      "line_id": "num-3",
      "filename": "numeric-num-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/numeric-num-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "牛顿法则借助切线，用导数指路，收敛得又快又准。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "拖动系数滑块，看曲线怎样上下起伏、左右摆动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "注意那些粉红色的根，如何随系数滑动、相遇甚至消失。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36576,
      "text": "求根就是找曲线与x轴的交点，n次多项式共有n个复根。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "实根看得见，复根成对藏，数值方法帮我们把它们一一逼近。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "polynomial-roots",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/polynomial-roots/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.33,
      "size": 37296,
      "text": "系数一动，根就起舞，这就是代数与几何的默契，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
